OL,4,Cquashed in two-minute hearing
OL,6,FTens of thousands of rail passengers
OL,7,Fwho wrongly faced court action for
OL,8,Fdodging rail fares have had their
OL,9,Fprosecutions quashed.
OL,11,FNorthern Rail brought 28,631
OL,12,Fprosecutions against passengers using
OL,13,Fthe single justice procedure (SJP)
OL,14,Fbetween August 6 2020 and May 21 2024,
OL,15,Fdespite not being permitted to do so.
OL,17,FTransPennine Express also brought 41
OL,18,Fprosecutions in January 2024.
