OL,3,C28,000 fare dodging prosecutions
OL,4,Cquashed in two-minute hearing
OL,6,FOn Thursday Chief Magistrate Paul
OL,7,FGoldspring declared them null and void
OL,8,Fduring a two-minute hearing at
OL,9,FWestminster Magistrates' Court.
OL,11,FFurther hearings will take place
OL,12,Fregarding thousands of other train
OL,13,Ffare prosecutions.
OL,15,FNorthern and TransPennine Express
OL,16,Fwelcomed Thursday's outcome and
OL,17,Fapologised for the "errors".
