OL,4,Cquashed in two-minute hearing
OL,6,FThe SJP was established in 2015 to
OL,7,Fallow magistrates to decide on minor
OL,8,Foffences. When a defendant pleads
OL,9,Fguilty, they do not need to attend
OL,10,Fcourt, and therefore most cases are
OL,11,Fheard in private.
OL,13,FRail companies were permitted to use
OL,14,Fthe SJP in 2016 to privately prosecute
OL,15,Ffare evaders, but many have been
OL,16,Fbrought under the Regulation of
OL,17,FRailways Act 1889, which is not
OL,18,Fallowed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/9
