OL,4,Cquashed in two-minute hearing
OL,6,FIn a ruling on six "test" cases in
OL,7,FAugust, Mr Goldspring said: "They
OL,8,Fshould never have been brought through
OL,9,Fthat process. This is, to my mind, a
OL,10,Fparadigm nullity."
OL,12,FAmong those who were wrongly
OL,13,Fprosecuted under the SJP system was
OL,14,FChristian Waters, from West Yorkshire.
OL,16,FHe was unable to buy a ticket at his
OL,17,Flocal station, Kirkstall Forge in
OL,18,FLeeds, in 2022 because the machine was
OL,19,Fbroken at the time.
