OL,4,Cquashed in two-minute hearing
OL,6,FHe received a penalty fare from
OL,7,FNorthern and ended up being taken to
OL,8,Fcourt.
OL,10,FChristian told ITV News in August: "I
OL,11,Fthought I'd either get (a ticket) on
OL,12,Fthe train or the excess fares booth in
OL,13,FLeeds. And then when I didn't see a
OL,14,Fconductor on the train, I got to the
OL,15,Fexcess fair window there was a group
OL,16,Fof revenue inspectors and they pulled
OL,17,Fme out of the queue and they gave me a
OL,18,Fpenalty fare.
