OL,6,F"I felt really annoyed, it's not the
OL,7,Ffirst time the machine hadn't been
OL,8,Fworking and I'd felt like a criminal."
OL,10,FIn identical statements, Northern and
OL,11,FTransPennine said: "Customers affected
OL,12,Fby the issues raised in court will be
OL,13,Fcontacted directly by HM Courts and
OL,14,FTribunal Service. We are unable to
OL,15,Frespond to individual queries at this
OL,16,Ftime.
