OL,6,F"Northern remains committed to
OL,7,Fensuring that all our customers are
OL,8,Ftreated fairly, which means ensuring
OL,9,Fall passengers who board our trains
OL,10,Fhave a valid ticket."
OL,12,FAffected cases were also prosecuted by
OL,13,FAvanti West Coast, Greater Anglia,
OL,14,FGreat Western Railway, Arriva Rail
OL,15,FNorthern, Merseyrail and C2C, the
OL,16,FCourts and Tribunals Service said.
