OL,6,FThe department said that those
OL,7,Faffected should wait to be contacted
OL,8,Fdirectly by the Courts and Tribunals
OL,9,FService about their case, including if
OL,10,Fthey have paid a financial penalty.
OL,12,FA Government spokesperson said: "While
OL,13,Ffare evasion should be tackled, the
OL,14,Fright process should be followed at
OL,15,Fall times.
OL,17,F"A consultation examining the Single
OL,18,FJustice Procedure and regulation of
OL,19,Fprivate prosecutors will drive up
OL,20,Fstandards."
