OL,7,Fpresident Richard Atkinson said: "We
OL,8,Fwelcome the Government's commitment to
OL,9,Freview the Single Justice Procedure as
OL,10,Fwe are aware concerns have been raised
OL,11,Ffor some time about how fairly the
OL,12,Ffast-track system operates,
OL,13,Fparticularly in regard to vulnerable
OL,14,Fpeople."
